casebody.head_matter:
Joanne STONE, petitioner,
v.
LOUISIANA DEPARTMENT OF REVENUE.
No. 17-7692.
Supreme Court of the United States
March 19, 2018.
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioner allowed until April 9, 2018, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules if this Court.
